msgctxt "QL_HatenoMini_BlueFire_Carry"
msgid ""
"You lit the furnace at the\n"
"Akkala Ancient Tech Lab with blue flame.\n"
"The ancient oven is now up and running\n"
"again.\n"
"\n"
"It's time to go tell Robbie."
msgstr ""

